    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756730/extras/3487b6c76f12eb1ca4741217abe8e3d8.avif?t=1764345672\" width=600 height=102 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756730/extras/4c37ad7d5f875b9461996f5ab9599b05.poster.avif?t=1764345672\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756730/extras/4c37ad7d5f875b9461996f5ab9599b05.webm?t=1764345672\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756730/extras/4c37ad7d5f875b9461996f5ab9599b05.mp4?t=1764345672\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Draft your forces among a wide variety of unique units, who each have a unique set of skills to exercise on the battlefield. Bully enemies by pushing and pulling them with the hearty Champion, strike and fade with the swift Cavalier, lay devastating traps with the talented Mage, and steal your opponent’s life essence and donate it to your companions as a Vampire healer. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756730/extras/5f1be8c7748e18205d17b5105dfd1517.avif?t=1764345672\" width=600 height=102 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756730/extras/a66e950b9ba064d13e8b12f47154a21d.poster.avif?t=1764345672\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756730/extras/a66e950b9ba064d13e8b12f47154a21d.webm?t=1764345672\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756730/extras/a66e950b9ba064d13e8b12f47154a21d.mp4?t=1764345672\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Units have complementary skill-sets that enable a pair to accomplish more together than they would alone. Well-coordinated skills can be greater than the sum of their parts!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756730/extras/5dc724c06cf44b12dca138cf9ca3fade.avif?t=1764345672\" width=600 height=102 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756730/extras/4616c9c91a129018420e8b84d1c329bd.poster.avif?t=1764345672\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756730/extras/4616c9c91a129018420e8b84d1c329bd.webm?t=1764345672\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756730/extras/4616c9c91a129018420e8b84d1c329bd.mp4?t=1764345672\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Exploit the terrain on the battlefield to gain the upper hand. Hold defensive positions, close drawbridges on unsuspecting enemies, or launch over walls to outflank your foes.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756730/extras/45cbc1fb3477ccd21bf56eb9ab282cd7.avif?t=1764345672\" width=600 height=102 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756730/extras/f4c5a8a12a9f4bb864e2e8800069995c.poster.avif?t=1764345672\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756730/extras/f4c5a8a12a9f4bb864e2e8800069995c.webm?t=1764345672\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756730/extras/f4c5a8a12a9f4bb864e2e8800069995c.mp4?t=1764345672\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Experience a fully-featured Campaign story that spans the continent, gathering companions to your Mercenary company, and take on challenges that grow ever greater. Fate has great (and terrible) things in store for you and your companions.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756730/extras/19ea3ad0884feed2c9ca6716feb177c8.avif?t=1764345672\" width=600 height=102 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756730/extras/6254ee141fecb104898c63afc888a9b9.poster.avif?t=1764345672\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756730/extras/6254ee141fecb104898c63afc888a9b9.webm?t=1764345672\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756730/extras/6254ee141fecb104898c63afc888a9b9.mp4?t=1764345672\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Missions can have multiple victory conditions, and you only need to meet one to win! When you’re on the back-foot, look for an opportunity to snatch victory from the jaws of defeat.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756730/extras/953f6e2fb93a8e2bc0819ff8b1698e6c.avif?t=1764345672\" width=600 height=102 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756730/extras/fe5d03273b8ea5225764a2dcb45ec716.poster.avif?t=1764345672\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756730/extras/fe5d03273b8ea5225764a2dcb45ec716.webm?t=1764345672\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756730/extras/fe5d03273b8ea5225764a2dcb45ec716.mp4?t=1764345672\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Each faction moves one unit at a time. You’ll have to react to the evolving state of the battlefield as you adapt to the changing situations.",
